子构成言论保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-calling-arab-lawmakers-terrorists-constitutes-protected-speech/00000190-7216-d0bf-a9fd-76fe366f0000</link><description>该声明是为了回应 UAL 议员 Waleed Alhwashla 要求取消国家宣教部长 Orit Strock 的豁免权，以便以煽动罪对她提出起诉，此前她在 5 月份称该党为“穿着西装、打领带、笑容甜美的恐怖分子”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:25:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-calling-arab-lawmakers-terrorists-constitutes-protected-speech/00000190-7216-d0bf-a9fd-76fe366f0000</guid></item><item><title>反对党领袖拉皮德称内塔尼亚胡计划解雇以色列总检察长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-says-netanyahu-planning-to-fire-israels-ag/00000190-720d-d129-afba-ffffb6570000</link><description>极右翼部长大卫·阿姆萨勒姆指责司法部长“竭尽全力推翻政府”。拉皮德警告内塔尼亚胡正在考虑解雇总检察长，并告诉他的政党的立法者，不排除任何选择，包括集体辞职</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-says-netanyahu-planning-to-fire-israels-ag/00000190-720d-d129-afba-ffffb6570000</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何应对勒庞领导的全国集会党可能赢得的极右翼法国大选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/how-israel-is-contending-with-a-potential-far-right-french-election-win-by-le-pens-party/00000190-6fe7-dbfd-a5d1-eff783700000</link><description>以色列现在需要权衡法国极右翼目前对以色列的立场、其反犹太主义根源以及法国犹太社区对其民族主义言论的恐惧，因为几十年来一直拒绝与法国极右翼建立任何官方关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 03:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/how-israel-is-contending-with-a-potential-far-right-french-election-win-by-le-pens-party/00000190-6fe7-dbfd-a5d1-eff783700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队准备结束加沙战斗，但未达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-set-to-wind-down-fighting-in-gaza-but-without-reaching-a-hostage-deal/00000190-6f9a-d0bf-a9fd-6ffa14f20000</link><description>关键问题将是如何让公众相信以色列已经实现了战争期间的目标，尽管哈马斯尚未被彻底击败，而且 120 名人质仍滞留在加沙。 ■ 以色列领导人对 Al-Shifa 获释一事进行指责医院院长，内塔尼亚胡时代的惨败象征</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 03:05:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-set-to-wind-down-fighting-in-gaza-but-without-reaching-a-hostage-deal/00000190-6f9a-d0bf-a9fd-6ffa14f20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，两名以色列士兵在加沙中部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-live/netanyahu-says-israel-close-to-eliminating-hamas-military/00000190-713b-d33f-a7b9-75bfb46f0000</link><description>两名以色列士兵在加沙中部的战斗中丧生 ■ 内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，政府不知道释放 Al-Shifa 医院院长的决定 ■ 以色列为加沙海水淡化和污水处理厂重新通电 ■ 本-格维尔呼吁辛贝特负责人辞职 ■ 据以色列国防军报道，火箭袭击加沙边境社区后，以色列军队连夜袭击了一些地点</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 02:25:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-live/netanyahu-says-israel-close-to-eliminating-hamas-military/00000190-713b-d33f-a7b9-75bfb46f0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院以色列新法官抨击种族灭绝听证会“在思想上不诚实”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-judge-at-icj-slammed-genocide-hearing-as-intellectually-dishonest/00000190-7027-d33f-a7b9-74b7be7f0000</link><description>佩雷斯学术中心院长罗恩·夏皮拉教授被吹捧为现任政府可能任命的最高法院法官，政府希望任命一名保守派法官</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 21:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-judge-at-icj-slammed-genocide-hearing-as-intellectually-dishonest/00000190-7027-d33f-a7b9-74b7be7f0000</guid></item><item><title>青少年被以色列国防军招募从事情报行动，然后因间谍活动被判入狱，起诉国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/teen-recruited-by-idf-for-intelligence-operation-then-jailed-for-espionage-sues-state/00000190-6fd6-d705-a7f5-ffffc0890000</link><description>双桅船。总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的新任军事部长罗曼·戈夫曼将军